'''伊莎贝拉·阿博特'''（{{lang-en|'''Isabella Aiona Abbott'''}}，{{bd|1919年|6月20日|2010年|10月28日|catIdx=Abbott}}），为 [[夏威夷|夏威夷]]教育家和[[民族植物学|民族植物学]]家，是第一位获得[[科学|科学]][[哲学博士|博士]]学位的[[夏威夷原住民|夏威夷原住民]]<ref name="sesq">{{cite news |title= Isabella Abbott |author= Michael Tsai |date= July 2, 2006 |newspaper= [[Honolulu_Advertiser|Honolulu Advertiser]] |url= http://the.honoluluadvertiser.com/150/sesq6abbott |accessdate= November 4, 2010 |archive-date= 2020-07-29 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200729084507/http://the.honoluluadvertiser.com/150/sesq6abbott |dead-url= no }}</ref>。她是太平洋[[藻类学|藻类学]]方面的权威专家
<ref>{{cite news |title= 'Seaweed lady' Isabella Abbott dies: Scientist studied algae at Hopkins Marine Station |date= November 17, 2010 |author= Kevin Howe |newspaper= [[Monterey_Herald|Monterey Herald]] |url= http://www.montereyherald.com/local/ci_16635188 |accessdate= December 8, 2010 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140201170240/http://www.montereyherald.com/local/ci_16635188# |archive-date= 2014-02-01 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>。

==早年==
阿博特于1919年6月20日生于[[夏威夷領地|夏威夷領地]][[茂宜岛|茂宜岛]][[哈纳|哈纳]]，名字为'''Isabella Kauakea Yau Yung Aiona'''，意思是“哈纳白色的雨”，昵称为“Izzy”。<ref name=stanford/> 她的父亲是华人，她的母亲是夏威夷原住民后裔。她的母亲教她辨认可以食用的海藻。<ref name=stanford>{{cite news |first= Louis |last= Bergeron |title= Isabella Abbott, world-renowned Stanford algae expert, dies at 91 |url= http://news.stanford.edu/news/2010/december/izzie-abbott-obit-120710.html |work= Stanford Report |publisher= [[Stanford_University|Stanford University]] |date= December 7, 2010 |accessdate= December 7, 2010 |archive-date= 2020-11-16 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201116211340/https://news.stanford.edu/news/2010/december/izzie-abbott-obit-120710.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>

阿博特在[[檀香山|檀香山]]长大，1937年毕业于{{link-en|卡美哈梅哈学校|Kamehameha Schools}}<ref name="sesq"/><ref name=stanford/>。她于1941年获得 [[夏威夷大学马诺阿分校|夏威夷大学马诺阿分校]][[植物学|植物学]]本科学位<ref name=stanford/>，1942年和1950年分别获得[[密歇根大学|密歇根大学]]植物学硕士学位和[[加州大学伯克利分校|加州大学伯克利分校]]博士学位<ref name=stanford/>。她丈夫唐纳德·普特南·阿博特（Donald Putnam Abbott）（1920–1986）[[动物学|动物学]]家，是她在夏威夷大学和加州大学伯克利分校的同学。他们夫妇二人移居[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[太平洋丛林_(加利福尼亚州)|太平洋丛林市]]，她丈夫在[[斯坦福大学|斯坦福大学]]{{link-en|霍普金斯海洋研究站|Hopkins Marine Station}}教她专业知识<ref>{{cite web|title=Memorial Resolution: Donald Putnam Abbott 1920–1986 |url=http://www-marine.stanford.edu/memorials/AbbottD.pdf |accessdate=December 8, 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100705143303/http://www-marine.stanford.edu/memorials/AbbottD.pdf |archivedate=2010-07-05}}</ref>。当时，社会很少考虑让女性获得学术职位，她边抚养自己的女儿，边研究加州沿岸海藻。她发明了把海囊藻加入蛋糕和咸菜等食物中的办法。<ref name=stanford/>

==学术生涯==
1969年，阿博特开始在霍普金斯海洋研究站夏季学期讲课。她编纂了一部关于{{link-en|蒙特瑞半岛|Monterey peninsula}}海藻的专著，后来，这部专著后来又将加州海岸海藻研究包括进去。1972年，斯坦福大学破格直接将她升为正教授。1982年，阿博特夫妇退休，回到夏威夷，伊莎贝拉·阿博特被夏威夷大学聘用，开始研究[[民族植物学|民族植物学]]，这是一门关于人与植物相互关系的学科。<ref name=stanford/>

阿博特编著了8部著作，发表了150余篇论文。她被视为夏威夷海藻领域的权威专家，被称作''[[Limu_(algae)|limu]]''（[[夏威夷语|夏威夷语]]里海藻的意思）。她以发现了200余种物种享有盛誉，多种物种以她的名字命名。<!--如{{link-en|松节藻科|Rhodomelaceae}} including the [[Rhodomelaceae|Rhodomelaceae]] family (red algae) genus of ''Abbottella''.--><ref>{{cite news |title= Pioneering professor is first lady of limu |work= Malamalama: The Light of Knowledge |publisher= University of Hawai{{okina}}i |author= Jennifer Crites |date= October 21, 2010 |url= http://www.hawaii.edu/malamalama/2010/10/isabella-abbott/ |accessdate= November 4, 2010 |archive-date= 2019-12-27 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20191227234254/http://www.hawaii.edu/malamalama/2010/10/isabella-abbott/ |dead-url= no }}</ref> 这使她被称为"海藻第一夫人"。

1997年，阿波特获得[[美国国家科学院|美国国家科学院]]颁发的{{link-en|吉尔伯特·摩根·史密斯奖|Gilbert Morgan Smith Medal}}<ref name=Morgan>{{cite web|title=Gilbert Morgan Smith Medal|url=http://www.nasonline.org/site/PageServer?pagename=AWARDS_gmsmith|publisher=National Academy of Sciences|accessdate=16 February 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110210141836/http://www.nasonline.org/site/PageServer?pagename=AWARDS_gmsmith|archivedate=2011年2月10日}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title= Long Story Short with Leslie Wilcox: Guest Isabella Abbott |date= June 17, 2008 |work= [[PBS_Hawaii|PBS Hawaii]] |url= http://www.pbshawaii.org/ourproductions/longstory_transcripts/LSS%20126%20Transcript%20-%20Isabella%20Abbott.pdf |accessdate= November 4, 2010 |archive-date= 2016-03-16 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160316170010/http://www.pbshawaii.org/ourproductions/longstory_transcripts/LSS%20126%20Transcript%20-%20Isabella%20Abbott.pdf |dead-url= no }}</ref>。2008年，她获得{{link-en|夏威夷土地和自然资源部|Hawai'i Department of Land and Natural Resources}}颁发的终身成就奖<ref>{{cite news |title= Dr. Isabella Abbott honored for lifetime devotion to coral reefs |work= [[KHNL|KHNL]] |date= August 27, 2008 |author= Cindy Cha |url= http://www.khnl.com/global/story.asp?S=8913004 |accessdate= November 4, 2010 |archive-date= 2012-06-30 |archive-url= https://archive.today/20120630074255/http://www.khnl.com/global/story.asp?S=8913004 |dead-url= yes }}</ref>。

自1980年起直至退休，阿博特任夏威夷大学G. P. Wilder植物学讲席教授，退休后任植物学退休教授<ref>{{cite web |title= Emeriti Faculty |work= University of Hawaii catalog |year= 2005 |url= http://www.catalog.hawaii.edu/05-06/pdf/565-572EmeritiFaculty.pdf |accessdate= November 4, 2010 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20060902105036/http://www.catalog.hawaii.edu/05-06/pdf/565-572EmeritiFaculty.pdf |archivedate= 2006年9月2日 }}</ref>。她还担任{{link-en|毕夏普博物馆|Bishop Museum}}理事会理事<ref>{{cite web|title=Dr. Isabella A. Abbott |work=University of Hawaii Botany department faculty profile |url=http://www.botany.hawaii.edu/faculty/abbott/ |accessdate=November 4, 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111026080459/http://www.botany.hawaii.edu/faculty/abbott/ |archivedate=2011-10-26}}</ref>。1997年11月，她与别人共同在{{link-en|檀香山星报|Honolulu Star-Bulletin}}发表文章，批评卡美哈梅哈学校信托人工作不力，使卡美哈梅哈学校得以重组<ref>{{cite news |url= http://archives.starbulletin.com/97/11/27/news/index.html |title= Schools' gross mismanagement must stop: Tyranny, distrust, poor decisions reign at Kamehameha |date= November 27, 1997 |author= Isabella Aiona Abbott, [[Winona_Beamer|Winona Beamer]], [[Gladys_A._Brandt|Gladys A. Brandt]], Roderick F. McPhree and Winona Ellis Rubin |newspaper= [[Honolulu_Star-Bulletin|Honolulu Star-Bulletin]] |accessdate= December 10, 2010 |archive-date= 2011-11-14 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20111114162806/http://archives.starbulletin.com/97/11/27/news/index.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

2005年，阿博特入选{{link-en|夏威夷杰出人才库|Living Treasure of Hawai'i}}<ref>{{cite news |title= Six named Living Treasures |date= January 16, 2005 |newspaper= [[Honolulu_Advertiser|Honolulu Advertiser]] |url= http://the.honoluluadvertiser.com/article/2005/Jan/16/ln/ln19p.html |accessdate= November 4, 2010 |archive-date= 2018-08-24 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180824034055/http://the.honoluluadvertiser.com/article/2005/Jan/16/ln/ln19p.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。2010年10月28日，阿博特在檀香山家中去世，享年91岁<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.staradvertiser.com/news/20101031_Algae_expert_meshed_science_and_native_culture.html |title=Algae expert meshed science and native culture |newspaper=[[Honolulu_Star-Advertiser|Honolulu Star-Advertiser]] |author=Leila Fujimori |date=October 31, 2010 |accessdate=November 4, 2010 |archive-date=2012-09-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120905132553/http://www.staradvertiser.com/news/20101031_Algae_expert_meshed_science_and_native_culture.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

